    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mutual Assured Destruction Simulator</strong> is a short and surreal dark comedy-horror narrative game. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It's your first day as a MAD Technician, and we're here to guide you through your training! But don't worry, it's all just a simulation...</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A rich narrative-driven experience.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fully voice acted.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple endings to discover.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Different achievements to unlock depending on your actions.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A unique two-button control scheme.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Confetti. Lots of confetti.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Warning: This game contains flashing lights, as well as audio and imagery that some people may find uncomfortable.</strong></p>",
